            %p The ImprovMasters Toastmasters club was established in 2006 and chartered in June 2012 as Club No. 2563285.  Most of our members hail from the west part of Los Angeles, but some members travel from other locations in the region. Our meetings are fun but structured. We always look forward to new smiling faces, so please feel free to join us and see what we’re all about.

            %p We meet every Friday from 8PM to 10PM at Share Building in the Serenity Conference Room (2nd Floor).  The address is 6666 Green Valley Circle, Culver City CA 90230.
